Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-sequence-python3, dh-sequence-sphinxdoc, libffi-dev, libgit2-dev (>= 1.7), libgit2-dev (<< 1.8~), libpython3-all-dev, python3-all-dev:any, python3-cffi:native, python3-pycparser:native, python3-pytest <!nocheck>, python3-setuptools, python3-six, python3-sphinx-rtd-theme:native <!nodoc>, python3-sphinx:native <!nodoc>
Description: Python bindings for libgit2 The Pygit2 module provides a set of Python bindings to the libgit2 shared library. libgit2 implements the core of Git. Pygit2 works with Python 2.7, 3.x and pypy.
Package-List: python-pygit2-doc deb doc optional arch=all python3-pygit2 deb python optional arch=any
